{"tid":1304365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【絕冇炒車】TVB確認曾回應《環球時報》  重申「公正不偏，不對暴力低頭」","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:51:09.000Z","uid":15696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b791cb3176a9f75f95bf67a6bcea43280d8f241","tid":1304365,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TVB確認曾回應《環球時報》 向內地傳媒表示受「不恰當打壓」</span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><br />\n確認《環時》報道 對港媒書面回應刪「打壓」「成磨心」字句</strong><br />\n<br />\n《香港01》記者向TVB查詢《環球時報》的說法是否準確，為何認為寶礦力討好示威者向暴力低頭。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">發言人確認《環球時報》的報道，但無補充。</span></span></strong>另外，TVB發言人給予中港兩地傳媒的書面回應，亦不一致，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB向內地傳媒表明外界對無綫「不恰當打壓」，「無綫電視成為磨心（兩面不討好）是意料之內」</span></strong></span>，但給香港傳媒的書面回應，則刪除此句。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/350461/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F350461%2F&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3f2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=9f7abdd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/350461/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/a5/CCTVB.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/340?cb=20090611060053\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Fa5%2FCCTVB.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F340%3Fcb%3D20090611060053&h=6dec5556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">CCTVB:我有回應 但回應不是公開聲明 <br />\n學777玩字眼 仆你個街</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong>THIS IS 100% REAL <br />\n(TVB回應環球時報原文)</strong><br />\n<br />\n本台(對《環球時報》)回應如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 本台對寶礦力昨天發表的公開信表示極度遺憾，特別是有關該公司要全面檢討對無線電視投放廣告的計劃，及促請無線電視響應公眾關注的言論。<br />\n<br />\n2. 近期在香港發生之示威及衝突事件中，無線電視新聞均實時以多角度畫面現場直播，讓觀眾第一時間了解現場實況。無線電視成為磨心(兩面不討好)，是意料之內。任何對無線電視不恰當的打壓，均不會影響本台<strong>公正不偏、客觀持平</strong>的新聞報道原則。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，TVB一名負責人在接受(《環球時報》)記者採訪時表示，TVB因為客觀報道香港發生暴力衝擊立法會事件，讓觀眾全面透過多角度畫面親眼目睹現場實況、了解了警察面對當時環境從而作出的行動，包括驅散示威者，同時TVB相關報道的收視率很高，影響力很大，因此受到示威者的針對。還有示威者在<strong>網上欺凌及恐嚇TVB的廣告客戶</strong>，要求他們撤銷投放在TVB的廣告。<br />\n<br />\n針對寶礦力水特撤銷投放在TVB的廣告一事，該負責人認為，寶礦力水特的言論可能是希望爭取示威者的支持，但其做法等同對暴力低頭。 法治是香港的基石，寶礦力水特是正當做生意，<strong>合法營商不應受到干預，不應也不能對暴力低頭。</strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"354483c6fd4d019cc1cd85eb6928797945f2c2e0","tid":1304365,"uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>同大陸傳媒就話:</strong><br />\n無綫電視成為磨心（兩面不討好），是意料之內。任何對無綫電視不恰當的打壓，均不會影響本台公正不偏、客觀持平的新聞報道原則。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>同香港傳媒就話:</strong><br />\n無綫電視的新聞採訪一直秉持中立、專業及客觀的原則，並確保報道準確及持平。於近期示威及衝突事件中，本台記者堅守崗位，第一時間在現場直播，透過提供多角度畫面讓觀眾親眼目睹現場實況，公正不偏報道事件。"},{"pid":"ce53f065b92833385acb938fbb133b5c0681ac0e","tid":1304365,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:00:06.000Z","msg":"炒車？】TVB：沒有發過此聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1303945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1303945</a><br />\n<br />\nTVB確認曾回應《環球時報》向內地傳媒表示受「不恰當打壓」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/350461/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F350461%2F&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3f2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=9f7abdd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/350461/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/26n6ziTEeDDbowBkQ/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26n6ziTEeDDbowBkQ%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a43b366a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2df7fbc40437d2c8989a443351c3d7ec44647529","tid":1304365,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"TVB唔好再請打手漂白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要回應《環球時報》又要唔想激嬲香港人"},{"pid":"4846194205c0ed89129778566c189fdc47d18346","tid":1304365,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:02:12.000Z","msg":"同蘋果就話冇發出聲明:<br />\n<br />\n【反紅媒】無綫否認曾發網傳版聲明 稱網民狙擊對公司業務並無重大影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190710/59809724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F59809724&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3f2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=f0478f5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F59809724&h=ac911130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190710/59809724</a><br />\n<br />\n同香港01就話《環球時報》的報道正確<br />\n<br />\nTVB確認《環時》報道 對港媒書面回應刪「打壓」「成磨心」字句<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/350461/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F350461%2F&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3f2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=9f7abdd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/350461/</a>"},{"pid":"daaa2803c4a84bde7a89df0c508fecaf703920c5","tid":1304365,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8AUfDFH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8AUfDFH.gif&h=de7aa6a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32562678db3e8b7cb587bf9b8b6a957ee6243a0e","tid":1304365,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://wariscrime.com/new/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/media-manipulation1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t